import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import App from "./App"
import { BrowserRouter } from "react-router-dom/cjs/react-router-dom.min"


ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
     <BrowserRouter>
     </BrowserRouter>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById("root")
)
